com.xatkit.core.interpreter

Interface OperationProvider

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ObjectOperationProvider

    public interface OperationProvider
    Provides concrete Operation instances from abstract OperationCalls.

    This provider allows to bind abstract operations to specific implementations, and can be implemented by any object to provide custom implementation of abstract operations to the interpreter.

    • Method Summary

      Operation getOperation(com.xatkit.common.OperationCall abstractOperation)
